meout errors as evidenced by increases in error ratios and client errors impacting frontend service performance.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService `client_error_ratio` peaked alongside Frontend `error_ratio` during the fault period, corroborated by trace latency data.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThis analysis supports the hypothesis that AdService's performance degradation, especially its latency and error handling issues, implicated in the observed anomalies in the frontend service, are likely to have been the root cause of the service disruptions during the specified period."}
